<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gradual-adj">gradual <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡrædʒuəl/    美 /'ɡrædʒuəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>逐渐的；逐步的；渐进的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 sudden </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As you go further south, you will notice a <strong>gradual change</strong> of climate.
继续向南走，你会注意到气候的逐渐变化。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The doctor said her weight loss should be gradual.
医生说她的体重应该慢慢减轻。</p><footer>北师大⑥ – 16</footer></div></div>